他也擔心，因為媒體的質疑，而會影響外商的投資意願，尤其一些新創公司，一剛開始也是名不見經傳，貿然質疑並不恰當。"},{"pid":"d52275f88a329898e1efd6217eafd0c01636bd09","tid":619986,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0c23172598b0e548ea1998d2d3f4321e131a4c8","tid":619986,"uid":130901,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"7867456a1231594e9532a1c588e503d51c152a88","tid":619986,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"香港：要買東江臭水，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:18:30.000Z","msg":"想解約仲難過有線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"少年 你太年輕了"},{"pid":"d961605c3c797d7893a146efeb40ae74ae91a77a","tid":619986,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"Taiwan no.1"},{"pid":"4177f543a95ff7130564f96fa902d54c1fe1b01f","tid":619986,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa9cb0cde3e0b237160db2fa8e82c36b8c8ed3e6","tid":619986,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"咪話左係老千局來咩？"},{"pid":"2a758a69d411e702bf5f3f086b567e369e7adb7b","tid":619986,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"767fae6a626d33d0817807a11ae1429dde97bf0e","tid":619986,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.harry-hoffmann.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.harry-hoffmann.com%2F&d=lRYOs8fSOO9nUw%2FeNYAX1pnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=8d48afaa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.harry-hoffmann.com/</a><br />\n間野個網好流下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"一聽就知流啦，2百幾萬噸礦物？2百幾公斤已經好撚勁，當然用電成本貴過收成幾千倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a188ea3f3204fd0e29ec8d596a219b59ae4b33b","tid":619986,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"s